description: BBQ Lunch Trailer Serving the Best Fresh Island Fare At Great Prices!Eat at Big Beach BBQ in Makena, Maui! Located on Makena Road just before the parking entrance to Big Beach  we serve Fresh Fish Tacos, Smoked Kalua Pork Sliders, Pineapple Sausages, Ice Cold Pineapple and more! All from locally grown produce and family recipes. ALOHA!Big Beach BBQ proudly supports our local Farmers & Fisherman.
